        <item>
            <title>0.4.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 23:30:51 +1000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4000</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.4.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><strong>What's new</strong><ul>
<li>Scan Macintosh HD button in the disk space menu bar popover</li>
<li>Live scan progress in the disk menu bar popover while identifying storage</li>
<li>Show DiskWise in Dock toggle in both disk and system status menu bar popovers</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Improvements</strong><ul>
<li>Fast scans run sequentially to reduce system load during identification</li>
<li>Health menu bar icon shows Good, Fair, or Poor instead of a numeric score; numeric score remains in the app</li>
<li>System status top processes show application names only, without full paths</li>
<li>Dashboard scan panel shows folder progress instead of parallel worker counts</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
]]></description>
